---
import SectionLayout from '../../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<SectionLayout title="Masterclasses" section="learning" activePage="masterclasses" description="Monthly masterclasses at La Loingtaine led by Aki Saulière for conservatory students.">
  <h2>Masterclasses</h2>
  <p class="page-intro">
    Monthly opportunities for conservatory students to develop their musical identity
    under the guidance of Aki Saulière.
  </p>

  <div class="masterclass-content">
    <p>
      The masterclasses at La Loingtaine offer a unique opportunity for young musicians
      to work on developing their <strong>personal musical identity</strong>. Beyond
      technique, students explore interpretation, phrasing, and the deeper qualities
      that transform a performance into a profound musical experience.
    </p>
    <p>
      Led by <strong>Aki Saulière</strong>, these monthly sessions provide individual
      attention in an encouraging and supportive environment. Students perform for
      their peers, receive detailed feedback, and gain insights that go beyond
      what traditional conservatory training can offer.
    </p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3>Masterclass Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Monthly (October – June)</li>
        <li><strong>Director:</strong> Aki Saulière</li>
        <li><strong>For:</strong> Conservatory-level string students</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> La Loingtaine, Montigny-sur-Loing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For information and registration, contact:
        <a href="mailto:info@laloingtaine.org">info@laloingtaine.org</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>

<style>
  .masterclass-content {
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .info-box {
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-burgundy);
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .info-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .info-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .info-box li {
    padding: var(--space-xs) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .info-box li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
</style>
